  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nCheckpointStateCache is designed to have 10 epoch maximum but it's used to be up to 14-16 epochs during non-finality time in prater as shown in the below metrics\r\n\r\n<img width=\"822\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-01-07 at 11 22 45\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/148491341-eebea884-9a8a-49a3-a49e-61734acc8655.png\">\r\n\r\nright now we prune per checkpoint, but if we have multiple skipped checkpoint slots then we'll not prune CheckpointStateCache for a while https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/d78d0c5790eb7010a8368698ff5d7f2cfb24331b/packages/lodestar/src/chain/blocks/importBlock.ts#L138\r\n\r\nwe should prune per epoch instead\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nMax 10 epochs in CheckpointStateCache",
